@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5249

### Get all weather stations
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations
Accept: application/json

### Filter stations by state (Florida)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations?state=CO
Accept: application/json

### Get a single station by ID (Denver)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/den01
Accept: application/json

### Get a single station by ID (Miami)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/mia01
Accept: application/json

### Get a station that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/xyz99
Accept: application/json

### Current conditions — Denver (dry, windy, high elevation)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/den01/conditions
Accept: application/json

### Current conditions — Miami (humid, tropical, rain)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/mia01/conditions
Accept: application/json

### Current conditions — Seattle (overcast, rainy)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/sea01/conditions
Accept: application/json

### Current conditions — Phoenix (extreme heat, clear)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/phx01/conditions
Accept: application/json

### Current conditions — Chicago (cold, snowy, windy)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/chi01/conditions
Accept: application/json

### Daily forecast — Denver, default 5 days
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/den01/forecast/daily
Accept: application/json

### Daily forecast — Miami, full 7 days
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/mia01/forecast/daily?days=7
Accept: application/json

### Daily forecast — Chicago, 3-day outlook
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/chi01/forecast/daily?days=3
Accept: application/json

### Hourly forecast — Phoenix, next 6 hours
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/phx01/forecast/hourly?hours=6
Accept: application/json

### Hourly forecast — Seattle, full 24 hours
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/sea01/forecast/hourly
Accept: application/json

### Hourly forecast — Denver, next 12 hours
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/den01/forecast/hourly?hours=12
Accept: application/json

### Air quality — Phoenix (Unhealthy for Sensitive Groups, high PM10)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/phx01/air-quality
Accept: application/json

### Air quality — Denver (Good)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/den01/air-quality
Accept: application/json

### Air quality — Miami (Moderate, elevated O3)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/stations/mia01/air-quality
Accept: application/json

### All active alerts across all stations
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts
Accept: application/json

### Alerts filtered to Warning severity and above
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts?minSeverity=Warning
Accept: application/json

### Alerts for Chicago only (winter storm + high wind)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts?stationId=chi01
Accept: application/json

### Alerts for Miami only (tropical storm + flood)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts?stationId=mia01
Accept: application/json

### Alerts for Denver (expect empty array — no active alerts)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts?stationId=den01
Accept: application/json

### Combined filter — Chicago, Warning+ severity only
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/weather/alerts?stationId=chi01&minSeverity=Warning
Accept: application/json

